(24912, 'Phragra 25 mg 4 f.c.tab.', 'فراجرا 25مجم 4 قرص', '', '9', 'Sildenafil', 'Pharco', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '25 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
